<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="at-the-thought-of">at the thought of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>一想起… (就)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was sad at the thought of leaving the house, as it was full of so many memories. 
一想到要离开这栋房子她就难过起来，因为这里充满了很多回忆。</p></div></div>